'''亞洲國際新聞'''（{{lang-en|Asian News International}}，{{lang|en|ANI}}）是一家总部位于[[印度|印度]][[新德里|新德里]]的印度[[通讯社|通讯社]]，它为印度及其他地区的众多新闻機構提供[[多媒體|多媒體]]新闻源<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=MHujEBLJcvIC&pg=PA63|title=News Agencies from Pigeon to Internet|last=Shrivastava|first=K. M.|date=2007|publisher=Sterling Publishers Pvt. Ltd|isbn=9781932705676|language=en|access-date=2021-02-16|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122084357/https://books.google.com/books?id=MHujEBLJcvIC&pg=PA63|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=sVffFCoGSuIC&pg=PA122|title=International News in the 21st Century|last=Paterson|first=Chris A.|last2=Sreberny|first2=Annabelle|date=2004|publisher=Georgetown University Press|isbn=9781860205965|page=122|language=en|access-date=2021-02-16|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120015321/https://books.google.com/books?id=sVffFCoGSuIC&pg=PA122|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Footaging It Fleetly|url=https://www.outlookindia.com/magazine/story/footaging-it-fleetly/288837|accessdate=2019-12-29|work=Outlook India Magazine|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805171255/https://www.outlookindia.com/magazine/story/footaging-it-fleetly/288837|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亞洲國際新聞由Prem Prakash於1971年12月9日創辦。截至2019年，它是印度最大的电视[[通讯社|通讯社]]。

